name: Delusional Anxiety
description:
This painting is a very personal piece that remind me
of those times when things were completely chaos,
seemed so bizarre, meaningless, too crowded, too noisy,
too complicated.
But at the same time telling me that even
the worst thing can possibly gets better.


Acrylic, alcohol ink & gouache on paper + digital. 

*Delusional anxiety is one of the symptoms ofSchizophrenia Paranoid.
